#   Stars      : 4
#   Language   : Rust  (docopt for CLI parsing + hyper for the
#                 HTTP server side + ldap3 for the LDAP-client
#                 side + lru_time_cache for the per-section
#                 LDAP-response cache + sha2 for cache-key
#                 derivation + secrecy for in-memory password
#                 secret handling + tokio for the async runtime)
#   Binary     : ldap_authz_proxy
#   Version    : 0.3.2
#   Last push  : 2026-05-06
